  "text": "To reconstruct isotropic x-space MPI images, we first reconstruct each collinear channel image separately using x-space reconstruction [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Following the algorithm presented in Eq. 13, we then normalize each reconstructed MPI image by the receive coil sensitivity, interpolated each image onto the same image-domain sampling density, and summed the images to form a composite isotropic-resolution image.",
